channel.title: A little woodcutting help please?
channel.description:
Since the woodcutting on my server was total junk, I'm making a better version. Could someone please tell me the ID's for each stump(the normal trees, oaks, willows, maples, yews, and mages; not looking for like evergreens), and the gfx ID for chopping(preferably the individual ones for bronze, iron, steel, black, mith, addy, and rune axes)?
Thanks.

item.title: A little woodcutting help please?

item.description:

Check the MoparScape Client 3.2 with Aryan for the object IDs, however, try ‘875’ for the woodcutting emote.
